gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 105, Rockets 104
gameRecap.excerpt: LeBron James went 1/2 from the line with 1.9 seconds remaining to lift the Lakers over the Rockets, 105-104. LeBron recorded a season-high 37 points, along with eight assists and six rebounds for the Lakers, with Anthony Davis adding 27 points and 10 rebounds in the victory. Alperen Sengun tallied 23 points, 10 rebounds and five assists for the Rockets in the losing effort. The Lakers improve to 8-6 in the regular season, while the Rockets fall to 6-5.
